leetcode/majority-element.html.body:
求众数 Majority Element题目思路&题解知识点分析求众数 Majority Element
题目

找出给定数组内的众数，众数含义=》在数组中出现的次数超过⌊ n/2 ⌋ 的数字。

以下为详细说明：
Given an array of size n, find the majority element. The majority element is the element that appears more than ⌊ n/2 ⌋ times.
You may assume that the array is non-empty and the majority element always exist in the array.
Example 1:
Input: [3,2,3]
Output: 3
Example 2:
Input: [2,2,1,1,1,2,2]
Output: 2
思路&题解
class Solution {
    public int majorityElement(int[] nums) {
        int count = 1;
        int maj = nums[0];
        for (int i = 1; i 
class Solution {
    public int majorityElement(int[] nums) {
        HashMap map = new HashMap();
            for (int i = 0; i  entry : map.entrySet()) {
                int newValue = entry.getValue();
                if (newValue > count) {
                    key = entry.getKey();
                    count = newValue;
                }
            }
            return key;
    }
}

class Solution {
    public int majorityElement(int[] nums) {
        for(int i = 1; i=0 && nums[j]>key){
                nums[j+1]=nums[j];
                j--;
            }
            nums[j+1]=key;
        }
        return nums[nums.length/2];
